(30, 0, 'Top site to host free', 7, 'Nithin Migo', 'Top sites helps developer for free hosting and domain which helps to develop once portfolio', '1597337512_a.jpg', '<p><strong>Top</strong> <strong>sites</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vercel</li>\r\n	<li>Github page</li>\r\n	<li>Firebase</li>\r\n	<li>000webhostapp&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>AWS</li>\r\n	<li>Infinity free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vercel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Vercel is one of best platform to host your static web site. In this github respotory helps in linking it and gets you a domain with vercel as sub domain</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Sign up</li>\r\n	<li>Connect your github account.</li>\r\n	<li>Select your respotory to be hosted.</li>\r\n	<li>Give a domain name you will get domain as yourproject.vercel.app</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Vercel helps in Next.js helps highly in cross platforms for developers</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Github</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Github is one of famous platform for developers. Github helps in uploading and free storing and maintanance of project sources and also in sharing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Github also provide a static page to be hosted on.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create an account</li>\r\n	<li>Create New resporatory</li>\r\n	<li>Upload your source using terminal or other methods</li>\r\n	<li>At setting go for live.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In this only one can be lived at a time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Firebase</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Firebase is google based developers platform. This provide us hosing, database support and many more. This needs few cmds to be processed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sign up with google account</li>\r\n	<li>Create a project and select hosting in sidebar</li>\r\n	<li>In your code source to be hosted run certain codes as firebase init</li>\r\n	<li>It creates firebase setup then select project created</li>\r\n	<li>Finally go for firebase deploy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Firebase also provide database services based on apis and other platforms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>000webhostapp&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;000webhostapp provides a good hosing for static and even for dynamic web apps with phpmyadmin. This is maintained by Hostinger. This gives links as yourdomain.000webhostapp.com</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Sign up for 000webhost</li>\r\n	<li>Create a domain select filemanager in tools</li>\r\n	<li>Upload your src using zip</li>\r\n	<li>For database in tools go for database and link it out</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>000webhostapp allows only one hostinger for an account which was two in past&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AWS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AWS is amazon web server platform which gives free hosting based on hours.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create an account&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>It requires credit card details to complete sign up</li>\r\n	<li>On sign up create a project and upload source files</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Infinity</strong> <strong>free</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Infinity free provides a wast hosting platform and database. This platform provide cpanel. Which makes it easy to upload and maintain. Database of phpmyadmin, postgransql ect.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sign up for free</li>\r\n	<li>Create a subdomain if you have domain you can go for it.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Submit it out to create a cpanel filemanager</li>\r\n	<li>Upload your source inside htdocs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This platform also provide subdomain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2020-08-13');

